      <biogHist id="md5-29d80b1ea24046f7256b44370ee8fa08">
        <p>Anthropologist, 1928-  .  Henry T. Lewis, Chair of the Department of Anthropology (1971-1975  and 1986-1990), was named full professor in 1977.  He has conducted research in fire ecology as  practiced by the native peoples of northern Alberta, from which he produced a documentary film on  the subject, The Fires of Spring, in 1978.</p>
      </biogHist>
